<br>
Mob = Forest hurricane lorok ( frog )<br>
Hitpoints = 23-25 thousand<br>
They hit for 600-800's .. thank god they can't crit!<br>
<br>
Spells i hit them with .. snare and Ice spear of solists<br>
<br>
Ice spear does 1440 with ID3.<br>
<br>
Partner .. 65 bard .. using dots.<br>
<br>
I snare mob at 98 percent .. I don't pull aggro.<br>
I concussion .. drops aggro by 400.<br>
I am on horse .. so no sit aggro.<br>
<br>
The mobs health hits 80% .. or has 19200 hitpoints left ( bard has done 4800 dot damage.<br>
I nuke once. 1440 damage.<br>
I concussion 3 times (no resist).. drop aggro by 1200 points.<br>
The mobs health hits 60 % (Bard has done 8160 damage in dots now, I have done 1440)<br>
I nuke for another 1440... I GET AGGRO??!!<br>
Not only did I get aggro .. It took 6 concussions to lose it! This was repeated multiple times.<br>
<br>
Am I not suppose to nuke?<br>
<br>
I went to hate and never got aggro once. I was nuking as normal and not using concussion at all.. and mobs have less hitpoints there, so I was obviously doing much higher percentage of the damage.<br>
<br>
I normally start nuking at 90 percent at a more frequent rate, and concussion less, and never get aggro.<br>
<br>
They must fix this .. otherwise, it would be better for me to just solo, since I end up kiting them all around anyway.<br>
<br>
It also appeared to take more mana to solo them last night after the bard left. I was scraping bottom a couple times where i normally have 30 percent left... Higher resists? ..a bit more hitpoints?.. just a weird night.. not sure.<br>
<br>
Aggro is messed though!<br>
