<br>
Wouldn't this batched patch make AoE groups more attractive?<br>
<br>
/humor off<br>
<br>
IMO, the new pathing really stinks in some cases and is actually improved in others.  Some places I found mobs were more willing to come straight toward me allowing me to avoid pulling additional mobs.  Other places I notcied bizarre pathing when pulling, like in Lguk for example.<br>
<br>
I'm only 52 ( I've been 52 for 2 years lol!) so I have no idea what higher level aggro is like. From reading the posts, it's obvious that they've really skewered the poodle with this.<br>
<br>
My wife's cleric was noticing the same heal lag bug last night as was mentioned previously.  That's aweful and MUST be fixed!<br>
<br>
That 100% FD is true, for sure, and it's a pain in the ass to FD pull now.<br>
<br>
Something tells me that Sony is going to drag their heels and keep us in the dark on getting this one fixed.  I sure hope not, I'm tired of my warrior dying because the damned heal lag bug!!!<br>
